org.apache.oodt.cas.pge.writers

Class VelocityMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.oodt.cas.metadata.Metadata
      • org.apache.oodt.cas.pge.writers.VelocityMetadata

  • public class VelocityMetadata
extends Metadata
    Wrapper around CAS Metadata object to provide Velocity template semantics, e.g., a get(String) method that allows for ${metadata.author} (the '.' is a call that Velocity then makes from the template to the get(String) method in the class.
    Author:
    pramirez
